translated: The Great Khali (The Great Khali), whose real name is Dalip Singh Rana, is an Indian professional wrestler born in 1972 in Dhiraina in Himachal Pradesh.
original: The Great Khali (le Grand Khali), de son vrai nom Dalip Singh Rana, est un catcheur indien né en 1972 à Dhirana, dans l'Himachal Pradesh.
